quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  11,38,"Himo moЖҙЖҙina laana kan. Tuma kala nde dental hoorewal rewi ka o moЖҙЖҙinta ton, Й“e jalkita mo. O maaki: \"Si on jalkitii men, menen kadi men jalkitoyay on wano jalkitirton [men non]"
  11,39,"Aray nde annduЙ—on ko hommbo lepte hoynayЙ—e aroyat e muuЙ—um, lepte duumiiЙ—e jippoo e makko"
  11,40,"Haa si yamiroore Amen nden aroyii, huЙ“Й“inirЙ—e Й—en fati, Men daali: \"Ronndo e makka kala nooneeji Й—iЙ—i resindirayЙ—i e Й“eynguure maa nden -si wanaa Й“en konngol lepte ngol adii e mu'un- e Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e\". GomЙ—inaano wonndude e makko si wonah seeЙ—aaЙ“e"
  11,41,"O maaki: \"WaЙ—Й—oree e makka Innde Alla ka dogugol makka e daragol makko. Pellet Joomi am ko Haforoowo HinnotooЙ—o"
  11,42,"Kan no dogida e maЙ“Й“e e mollooЙ—e waaЙ—e wa pelle. Nuuhu noddi Й“iЙ—Й—o makko on, hari on no serindi: \"Ko an yo Й“inngel am, waЙ—Й—ida e amen, wata a wonndu e yedduЙ“e Й“en"
  11,43,"O wi'i: \"Mi Жҙawoyay e fello daЙ—ndayngo lam ndiyam Й—am\". O maaki: \"DaЙ—oowo yamiroore Alla nden alaa hannde si wanah on Mo O yurmini\". Molloonde nden heedi hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, o laatodii e yoolaaЙ“e Й“en"
  11,44,"Wi'a: \"Ko an yo leydi, moЙ—u ndiyam maa Й—am! Ko an kadi yo kammu, jogito [sorombooji ndiyam Й—in]!\". Ndiyam Й—am Й“eeЙ“i, fiyaaku on Гұaawaa, [laana] kan daroyii ka dow fello juudiiy, wi'aa: \"Halkaare woodanii Й“en yimЙ“e tooГұuЙ“e"
  11,45,"Nuuhu noddi Joomi makko, o maaki: \"Joomi am, pellet Й“iЙ—Й—o am on ko jeyaaЙ—o e Й“eynguure am, pellet fodoore Maa nden ko goonga. Ko An Й“uri nunЙ—ude Гұaawoore ГұaawooЙ“e"
